categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: Striker One was the callsign of a male pilot of the Galactic Republic living during the Galactic War. During the Battle of Corellia in 3640 BBY he commanded a wing of bombers that assisted Havoc Squad during their assault on the Bastion.
Striker One appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic during the Trooper class mission on Corellia.
